{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"colorBorderHover"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@OUDSTokensSemantic@objc(cs)MultipleColorSemanticToken","text":"MultipleColorSemanticToken"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeinputtagcomponenttokensprovider\/colorborderhover"]}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"colorBorderHover"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@OUDSTokensSemantic@objc(cs)MultipleColorSemanticToken","text":"MultipleColorSemanticToken"}],"title":"colorBorderHover","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"extendedModule":"OUDSThemesOrange","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B36ThemeInputTagComponentTokensProviderC16colorBorderHover18OUDSTokensSemantic013MultipleColorM5TokenCvp","roleHeading":"Instance Property"},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider\/colorBorderHover"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Has for value token colors.actionHover"}],"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider"}],"title":"OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeinputtagcomponenttokensprovider","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of tag input"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSInputTag"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllInputTagComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"InputTagComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tag inputs"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tag inputs"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and borders (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider/colorBorderHover":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"colorBorderHover","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"colorBorderHover"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@OUDSTokensSemantic@objc(cs)MultipleColorSemanticToken","text":"MultipleColorSemanticToken"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Has for value token colors.actionHover"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeinputtagcomponenttokensprovider\/colorborderhover","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider\/colorBorderHover","role":"symbol"},"ic_theme_orange.png":{"type":"image","alt":null,"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"Theme Orange","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","role":"collection"}}}